      "content": "hey i've been having such a hard time sleeping lately. i've been taking melatonin every night but it just isn't doing the trick anymore. my doctor just prescribed me some zolpidem (ambien) to help with the insomnia. do u think it's okay if i take the melatonin and the zolpidem at the same time? i'm hoping the combo will actually knock me out so i can finally get some rest.",
